column16: DJ LeMahieu flies out to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.
Matt Garza grounds out softly, pitcher Michael Fiers to first baseman Prince Fielder.    Bryan LaHair to 2nd.
Alfonso Soriano grounds out, shortstop Yuniesky Betancourt to first baseman Prince Fielder.
Carlos Gonzalez strikes out swinging.  Mark Ellis steals (12) 2nd base.
Mark Ellis singles on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Braun.    Dexter Fowler to 3rd.
Eric Young singles on a line drive to right fielder Corey Hart.
